sp.p:
Excellent News, my dear Mother-in-Law! At the coming in of the Brazil-Fleet, I will give you an Ingot of Gold to make a—Chocolate Mill on— Thank my Stars! The Ceremony of Courtship is over;

it has crack'd more Brains than Projecting and Poetry has done. Dear Angel
(to Victoria.) Let me Salute the hard Knuckles of your soft Hand.
